# ===============================
# Backend Deprecated
# ===============================
# This Express + MongoDB backend is no longer in use.
# The project has migrated to Supabase for database, auth, and REST API.
#
# See Frontend/.env for required environment variables:
#   - VITE_SUPABASE_URL
#   - VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#
# See Frontend/src/lib/supabase.js for the Supabase client setup.
#
# The Backend_legacy folder contains the archived Express server code.
# If you need to restore this backend, use Backend_legacy/.
